==Описание==

The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter|Spreadsheet AlignVCenter]]}} tool makes the text inside the cell align vertically to the center of the cell.

==Применение==

# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select a cell.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter|Spreadsheet AlignVCenter]]}} button.


